WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.640
[Amit Varma]: It's been 70 years since India became an independent country and my god what we've

00:00:08.640 --> 00:00:13.440
[Amit Varma]: had to get through to get here. There were so many challenges that we faced, so many barriers

00:00:13.440 --> 00:00:19.440
[Amit Varma]: that we needed to overcome to stay one united country. We were divided by language, ethnicity,

00:00:19.440 --> 00:00:27.200
[Amit Varma]: religion and most of all, perhaps the deepest division of all, by caste. And now 70 years after

00:00:27.200 --> 00:00:37.040
[Amit Varma]: we became independent, caste remains our greatest shame. Welcome to The Seen and The Unseen,

00:00:37.040 --> 00:00:42.320
[Unknown]: our weekly podcast on economics, politics and behavioral science. Please welcome your host,

00:00:42.320 --> 00:00:49.120
